{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "a4f7ca3d-2af9-43d3-9f3f-b005fa1ce3de", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/a4f7ca3d-2af9-43d3-9f3f-b005fa1ce3de@4.pkg/1772602105943/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602106161", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/a4f7ca3d-2af9-43d3-9f3f-b005fa1ce3de@4.pkg/1772602105943/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602106161"}, "identifier": "a4f7ca3d-2af9-43d3-9f3f-b005fa1ce3de", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>A.有误，“胆怯”的“怯”应读作“qiè”，“震聋发聩”的“震”应写作“振”。B.有误，“沼泽”的“沼”应读作“zhǎo”，“长途拔涉”的“拔”应写作“跋”。C.有误，“枯躁”的“躁”应写作“燥”，“张目结舌”的“结”应读作“jié”。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列词语中加点字的字音、字形完全正确的一项是（</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>）</span>​</p>\n", "label": "", "title": "下列词语中加点字的字音、字形完全正确的一项是（  ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/a4f7ca3d-2af9-43d3-9f3f-b005fa1ce3de@4.pkg/item.json?v=1748412381388", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "